This artifact is an AUTHORED Patronus instruction describing how a coding agent
should use the Ticket (`tk`) work-graph in a downstream project. It is NOT a
reproduction of upstream Ticket documentation.

The `tk` command surface and the work-graph usage model described in
INSTRUCTIONS.md are summarized from the upstream project's README and the
`ticket` script's own command dispatcher at the pinned commit.

The `tk` script itself is delivered by the sibling `tk` recipe (source: url,
pinned to the commit + sha256). This instruction `requires: [tk]`.

